Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:06.79,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們不要被條框鎖住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:11.47,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:29.97,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了像今天這樣的日子才叫生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:40.59,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}有了你就能一起踏過所有的困難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.61,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我相信 我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.53,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}戀愛笨蛋 看不清眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}束手無策 在這深夜裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:57.71,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}走投無路 遵守著約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:03.30,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}在自己鏡中留下投影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:10.14,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我們不要被條框鎖住的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:14.76,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}即使是拼湊的時光又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:21.15,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}向左向右都通向告別 這種答案毫無意義
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:26.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}我只會繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:29.95,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}直到遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:22:00.97,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}看看地獄之底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:08.54,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}小心別墮落下去 我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:23.82,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行屍走肉般走過的路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:29.33,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}頭頂的陽光分外刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.54,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不知何時你已經淪落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:40.25,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}連自己名字也都遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:44.46,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}究竟人類 為何而活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.13,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}哪怕生命 流逝消磨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.04,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}這無盡的煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:56.75,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}不如隨之起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:57.74,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:09.16,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}從寸草不生的山谷向上攀爬 聽風帶來山林的迴響
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:14.89,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}請看 指引我們的快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:20.01,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}就是斬斷悲哀的原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:24.62,OPEDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}別害怕 別顫抖 活下去

Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,// OPEDJ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.83,0:00:06.79,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}がんじがらめの自由なんて僕たちはいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:11.47,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}つぎはぎだらけな中で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:29.97,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}今日みたいな日があるから　生きていけるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:33.62,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}って思う　って思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:40.59,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}君って人がいるから　越えていけるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:44.61,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}って思う　って思う
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.53,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}愛の馬鹿　視界不良
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:53.71,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}どうしろって言うんだ　この夜に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.01,0:00:57.71,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}行き止まり　で指切り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:03.30,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}自分の鏡に　映し出せよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:10.14,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}がんじがらめの自由なんて僕たちはいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.51,0:01:14.76,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}つぎはぎだらけな中で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:21.15,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}さよならだけしか見つけられない答えなんてつまらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:26.33,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}会えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:29.95,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}探すから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:22:00.97,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}地獄の底まで覗きこめ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:08.54,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}腐敗ちて行くな　同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:23.82,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}死体みたいに歩く道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.26,0:22:29.33,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}ギラギラと太陽が照りつける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.44,0:22:34.54,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}おまえは何時か名前さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.95,0:22:40.25,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}分からなくなるくらい堕ちてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.20,0:22:44.46,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}人は　何故生きるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.91,0:22:48.13,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}生命　切り刻んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.69,0:22:52.04,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}終わりなき煩悩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.81,0:22:56.75,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}抱いて踊れば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:57.74,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}無常花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:09.16,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}渇きの谷から攀じ登れ　風の音が木霊して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:14.89,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}ご覧　我らを導く快楽は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.28,0:23:20.01,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}悲しみを突っ切っていく原理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:24.62,OPEDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2\be2\bord2}恐れるな　震えるな　生きるのだ